  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>1.17.11 is a minor update including some small features and bug fixes.</p><p>Scheduled for 11:30 CT on Aug 10, 2020</p><h3 id=\"id-1.17.11-EnhancementsandBugFixes\">Enhancements and Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Updated the ordering of ticket items on printed receipts so that child items in a bundle are always shown together with their parent, regardless of when the child item was added to the ticket.</p></li><li><p>Added the ability to more effectively delete holidays in settings.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a bug with handling of payment declines where electronic signatures are captured.</p></li><li><p>Adjusted the status flow for backorders to enable the following transitions:</p><ul><li><p>Pending Notifiction to In Repair</p></li><li><p>Pending Notification to Repair Completed</p></li><li><p>On Hold to Repair Completed</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
